        "evidence": "<p>The AUB-HAS2 is calculated by the addition of the selected points:</p>\n<table style=\"width: 100%; height: 456.547px; border-width: 1px; border-style: none;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3984px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 22.3984px; width: 78.9598%;\" colspan=\"3\"><strong>Variable</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 21.0402%; height: 22.3984px;\"><strong>Points</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3984px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 44.7968px; width: 25.0591%;\" rowspan=\"2\">Age, years</td>\n<td rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width: 34.279%; height: 44.7968px;\"></td>\n<td style=\"width: 19.6217%; height: 22.3984px;\">&lt;75</td>\n<td style=\"width: 21.0402%; height: 22.3984px;\">0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3984px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 19.6217%; height: 22.3984px;\">&ge;75</td>\n<td style=\"width: 21.0402%; height: 22.3984px;\">1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3984px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 44.7968px; width: 25.0591%;\" rowspan=\"2\">Hemoglobin, g/dL</td>\n<td style=\"height: 44.7968px; width: 34.279%;\" rowspan=\"2\"></td>\n<td style=\"width: 19.6217%; height: 22.3984px;\">&ge;12 g/dL</td>\n<td style=\"width: 21.0402%; height: 22.3984px;\">0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3984px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 19.6217%; height: 22.3984px;\">&lt;12 g/dL</td>\n<td style=\"width: 21.0402%; height: 22.3984px;\">1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 138.688px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 277.383px; width: 25.0591%;\" rowspan=\"2\">History of heart disease</td>\n<td style=\"height: 277.383px; width: 34.279%;\" rowspan=\"2\">e.g. history of previous myocardial infarction, coronary angioplasty, cardiac surgery, heart failure, atrial fibrillation, or moderate/severe valvular disease confirmed by echocardiography</td>\n<td style=\"width: 19.6217%; height: 138.688px;\">No</td>\n<td style=\"width: 21.0402%; height: 138.688px;\">0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 138.695px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 19.6217%; height: 138.695px;\">Yes</td>\n<td style=